Powered by a 5.6 Liter V8 that generates 305hp while paired with a 5 Speed Automatic transmission for plenty of towing power. This Four Wheel Drive combination delivers near 19mpg. You'll appreciate all this truck has to offer with its bright fog lamps, running boards, grille guard, and tow hitch.This XE comes with a spacious interior with two-tone cloth seating, cruise on the wheel, air conditioning and an AM/FM stereo with CD changer, AUX port, and available satellite radio.
